{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"title":"OUDSButton","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents10OUDSButtonV","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text with icon."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(icon:accessibilityLabel:hierarchy:style:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(icon:text:hierarchy:style:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(text:hierarchy:style:action:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/Hierarchy","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/Style"],"title":"Enumerations","generated":true,"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Hierarchies","text":"Hierarchies"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Five hierarchies are proposed for all layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default (by default)"}]},{"text":": Default buttons are used for actions which are not mandatory or essential for the user.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"strong","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Should be singular and prominent, limited to one per view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It should be reserved for the most critical action, such as “Next,” “Save,” “Submit,” etc. It is a “call for action”.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"brand"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A brand primary color alternative to the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"strong","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" button."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be used sparingly for high-value specific actions or to visually anchor a brand moment. Do not use it as the default primary button in your interfaces."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A button with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Brand"},{"type":"text","text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"minimal","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Minimal buttons are commonly used for actions that are considered less crucial. They can be used independently or together with a strong button.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Negative buttons should be used sparingly to warn of a destructive action,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for example, delete or remove, typically resulting in the opening of a confirmation dialog."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A button with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative"},{"type":"text","text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), hierarchy: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\")) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative,  style: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ A loading button","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", style: .loading) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text and icon with strong hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), text: \"Validate\", hierarchy: .strong) { \/* the action to process *\/ }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Styles","text":"Styles"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Two style are available:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default (by default)"}]},{"type":"text","text":": used in the normal usage of button. The aspect of the button changes for  states "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"disabled"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"pressed","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"hovered","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or normal (i.e. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"enabled","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"loading","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": used after button was clicked and probably data are requested before navigate to a next screen or get updated data."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Rounded-layout","text":"Rounded layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Buttons can have rounded layouts to be favored in more emotional, immersive contexts or those tied to specific visual identities."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For standard or business-oriented journeys, keep the default corners."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This evolution addresses the need for flexibility in adapting the design to some brand contexts."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To activate the rounded button behavior, set to true the  "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsRoundedButton"},{"type":"text","text":" environment variable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"at the root level of the view hierarchy (i.e. can be applied on the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to be sure all buttons in the application are rounded."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Add themeable view to your app root view to use the OrangeTheme","    OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","        YourRootView() \/\/ With some views with Buttons","    }","    .environment(\\.oudsRoundedButton, true)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Colored-surface","text":"Colored surface"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If button is placed on colored surface using ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrome mode.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remark: Today it is not allowed to place a Negative nor a Brand button on a colored surface."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Specific-behavior","text":"Specific behavior"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For accessibility reasons, if the system settings for reducing motion is enabled, the loading indicator does not move."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For ecodesign reasons, if the device is in low power mode, the loading indicator does not move."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/48a788-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"headin